snippet.title: FNAC FUR Teaser
snippet.description:
A new fun adventure with Candy and Co. based on the minigame Candy's Adventure from Five Nights at Candy's 3. Coming soon in the future!

This is a reupload of the teaser as it appeared on my Security Breach stream which you can watch here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cUolVxoatKs
